msgstr ""
"Este software é fornecido pelo autor 'como está' Y CUALQUER GARANTIA "
"EXPLÍCITA, incluindo as implícitas de comercialização e adequação para um "
"propósito determinado. No ent01/2023 05:04:00 PM | "
"https://www.deepl.com/translator#6f9b7a8d-bfed-4bdf-aeff-cbb4a9db5ece "
"Translation Memory (TM) is a technology that stores previously translated "
"text segments to aid human translators and machine translation systems in "
"producing consistent, accurate, and efficient translations. It works by "
"comparing new texts with existing translations stored within the memory or "
"database of an organization's internal system. This can significantly speed "
"up repetitive tasks for professional translators who often work on similar "
"content across different projects but may not be as effective when dealing "
"with highly specialized jargon, idiomatic expressions unique to a specific "
"field like legal documents in Portuguese-speaking countries or technical "
"manuals that require precise terminology. TM can also help maintain "
"consistency within large translation teams by ensuring uniformity of terms "
"and phrases across multiple translators working on the same project."

